Extended version: At the end will add the Chorus of another song called Evidence by Josh Baldwin:               "I see the evidence of your goodness. All over my life. All over life. I see your promises in fulfillment. All over my life. All over my life."                                            
 Repeated several times. The will go back to the Bridges and Chorus and then end the song.

Michelle Lead throughout 
Verse 1-Michelle starts solo, then Kristina duet at “From the moment that I wake up” 
Verse 2- All in: Michelle lead. Kristina-harmony 
Chorus x2-Michelle lead. Kristina-Harmony 
Bridge: x2- all in-unison then add harmony 
Chorus x 2 & Tag: Michelle melody; Kristina- harmony
Add new lyrics: I see the evidence of your goodness…
End: Chorus- quiet
